RESOURCE_TEXT_10203.ContentEN:
"I lit the first candle — I saw a voiceless youth;
I lit the second candle — I saw a blinded believer;
I lit the third candle — I saw a devout divine envoy.
The tender glow, carrying hymns, brushed past my eyes,
And I realized, each candle revealed a version of myself."

— A Nameless Divine Envoy Lost in the Abyss

